    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265520/extras/12ccc5a902f522121653b89e8dabd8c6.poster.avif?t=1771439536\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265520/extras/12ccc5a902f522121653b89e8dabd8c6.webm?t=1771439536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265520/extras/12ccc5a902f522121653b89e8dabd8c6.mp4?t=1771439536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay Objective:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get the Star safely to the Ground</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Click on other Blocks to remove them or interact with them</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let Gravity and Physics do its work</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Success!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265520/extras/3411a2fea38c97796c9553529759248d.poster.avif?t=1771439536\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265520/extras/3411a2fea38c97796c9553529759248d.webm?t=1771439536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265520/extras/3411a2fea38c97796c9553529759248d.mp4?t=1771439536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Versus Mode</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get your Star to the Ground to score a point</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Knock your opponents Star off to also score a point</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obstruct your opponent by sending them your blocks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pure Chaos</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First to 10 Points Wins!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265520/extras/f23c01eab776ce25410a35d242b97c93.poster.avif?t=1771439536\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265520/extras/f23c01eab776ce25410a35d242b97c93.webm?t=1771439536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265520/extras/f23c01eab776ce25410a35d242b97c93.mp4?t=1771439536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Level Editor &amp; Online Levels:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Level Sizes and Visual Styles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various fun Game Mechanics (Hazards, Bombs, Moving Platforms, Portals &amp; More)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make fun, creative and exciting levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upload and Share your level with others online</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play levels made by others!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265520/extras/d5054923701a86fdf9d94b5fc1f6e9cc.poster.avif?t=1771439536\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265520/extras/d5054923701a86fdf9d94b5fc1f6e9cc.webm?t=1771439536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265520/extras/d5054923701a86fdf9d94b5fc1f6e9cc.mp4?t=1771439536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >150 Arcade Levels to Challenge your Wits across 5 Unique Worlds!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Versus Mode: Play against a Friend!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 Extra Bonus Levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level Editor: Create and share your own unique levels with friends!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Block Database: Play more levels online from around the world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special unlocks: Achievements, Music &amp; Art</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cross Play &amp; Cloud Saves - Continue your game on any other device</p></li></ul>",
